        "subject": "LU-16806 lod: access DMV when it's valid",
        "message": "LU-16806 lod: access DMV when it's valid\n\nlod_declare_create() may access default LMV to check whether child\nis created on wrong MDT, if default LMV doesn't exist, this may\nlead to -EREMOTE error because the code doesn't check whether default\nLMV is valid.\n\nSigned-off-by: Lai Siyao <lai.siyao@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I5325b11a748b79d4a1aea42c7dcd37dad2438d6b\n"
